                  "id": "ja_ch1_f1",
                  "title": "Sets Laws & Relation Properties Cheat Sheet",
                  "content": "De Morgan's Laws:\n1. (A U B)' = A' n B'\n2. (A n B)' = A' U B'\n\nNumber of elements:\nn(A U B) = n(A) + n(B) - n(A n B)\n\nRelation R on Set A is Equivalence if:\n- Reflexive: (a, a) in R\n- Symmetric: (a, b) in R => (b, a) in R\n- Transitive: (a, b), (b, c) in R => (a, c) in R"
                }
              ],
